sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant FE as React Frontend
    participant Leaflet as Leaflet Map Canvas
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant ReportSvc as Report Service<br/>(WeasyPrint + Jinja2)
    participant KMLSvc as KML Service<br/>(simplekml)
    participant DB as MongoDB

    Note over User, DB: PDF Report Generation
    User->>FE: Click "Generate Report"
    FE->>Leaflet: Capture map as base64 PNG<br/>(leaflet-image)
    Leaflet-->>FE: map_image_base64

    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/projects/{id}/report<br/>{ map_image_base64, include_coverage_stats }
    API->>DB: Fetch Project metadata
    API->>DB: Fetch CameraInstances[]
    API->>DB: Fetch Zones[]
    DB-->>API: All project data

    API->>ReportSvc: generate_pdf(project, cameras, zones,<br/>map_image_base64, coverage_stats)
    ReportSvc->>ReportSvc: Render Jinja2 HTML template<br/>(map image · camera table · coverage summary)
    ReportSvc->>ReportSvc: WeasyPrint HTML → PDF bytes
    ReportSvc-->>API: PDF bytes

    API-->>FE: application/pdf stream<br/>Content-Disposition: attachment
    FE->>FE: Trigger browser download<br/>{project_name}_report.pdf

    Note over User, DB: KML Export
    User->>FE: Click "Export KML"
    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/projects/{id}/export/kml
    API->>DB: Fetch CameraInstances + Zones
    DB-->>API: cameras[] + zones[]
    API->>KMLSvc: generate_kml(cameras, zones)
    KMLSvc->>KMLSvc: Camera positions → KML Placemarks
    KMLSvc->>KMLSvc: FOV polygons → styled KML Polygons
    KMLSvc->>KMLSvc: Zones → KML Polygon / LineString
    KMLSvc-->>API: .kml file bytes

    API-->>FE: application/vnd.google-earth.kml+xml<br/>Content-Disposition: attachment
    FE->>FE: Trigger browser download<br/>{project_name}.kml
